guageName":{"simpleText":"Kri"}}],"defaultAudioTrackIndex":7}},"videoDetails":{"videoId":"sTzf5UEi4P4","title":"This Advice Impacted 10,000,000 People (Jim Rohn Seminar)","lengthSeconds":"788","keywords":["jim rohn","jim rohn motivation","personal development","jim rohn seminar","inspiration","inspirational","motivational","change your life","success mindset","jim rohn philosophy","motivational video","jim rohn life advice","personal growth","motivational speech","jim rohn lectures","jim rohn speech","success habits","jim rohn real seminar","work on yourself","the advice that touched 10000000 people","jim","rohn","change","thank me in 7 days","advice","everything will change","life advice","motivation"],"channelId":"UC2r0MaYV4ni7rilxvcjZ-mg","isOwnerViewing":false,"shortDescription":"In this powerful motivational talk, Jim Rohn breaks down four major lessons that can elevate you beyond the average and into a life of purpose, discipline, and true value. These aren’t shortcuts, they’re timeless principles that shape how you think, act, and grow.\n\nA timeless message from Jim Rohn®\n\nThis timeless message will challenge your thinking, reshape your habits, and show you how real change begins from within.\n_____________\n\n➤Speaker: Jim Rohn\nhttps://www.jimrohn.com/\n\nJim Rohn (1930–2009) was a world-renowned motivational speaker, author, and personal development expert. He inspired millions with his lessons on discipline, mindset, and taking consistent action to achieve success. Known as the 'mentor to the mentors,' Rohn directly influenced some of today's most popular speakers such as Tony Robbins and Brian Tracy.\n\n_____________\n\n➤SUCCESS® presents: Jim Rohn®. To discover more powerful messages and timeless teachings from Jim Rohn, visit: https://www.success.com/subscriptions/\n\n➤Licensed for use from https://mindsetdrm.com/\n\n#jimrohn #personaldevelopment #motivation","isCrawlable":true,"thumbnail":{"thumbnails":[{"url":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/sTzf5UEi4P4/hq