te you beyond the average and into a life of purpose, discipline, and true value. These aren’t shortcuts, they’re timeless principles that shape how you think, act, and grow.\n\nA timeless message from Jim Rohn®\n\nThis timeless message will challenge your thinking, reshape your habits, and show you how real change begins from within.\n_____________\n\n➤Speaker: Jim Rohn\nhttps://www.jimrohn.com/\n\nJim Rohn (1930–2009) was a world-renowned motivational speaker, author, and personal development expert. He inspired millions with his lessons on discipline, mindset, and taking consistent action to achieve success. Known as the 'mentor to the mentors,' Rohn directly influenced some of today's most popular speakers such as Tony Robbins and Brian Tracy.\n\n_____________\n\n➤SUCCESS® presents: Jim Rohn®. To discover more powerful messages and timeless teachings from Jim Rohn, visit: https://www.success.com/subscriptions/\n\n➤Licensed for use from https://mindsetdrm.com/\n\n#jimrohn #personaldevelopment #motivation","commandRuns":[{"startIndex":457,"length":24,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CM0BEM2rARgBIhMI9_Oixf2XlAMVAIx8Bh2_zxTnSP7Bi4nU_LeesQHKAQRCvdcg","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqa3pvRldraHprZU9CNkRrSVMwYjA3dzdsVkVLd3xBQ3Jtc0tuMG9MOUo4aktGeHRadTZYdUpKM3N3OHNyQl9ObXdKR2dRZWwyMzBtZW15Q1FnUTRuSEJaRmFkbjctUVF2U2VTWGc5cU1DZ0pEblk2ZTE5eDNDeFBnRjlEQ01PeW5udVNFMzhRZlVPX1hpR2ZFRVpNUQ\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jimrohn.com%2F\u0026v=sTzf5UEi4P4","webPageType":"WEB_PAGE_TYPE_UNKNOWN","rootVe":83769}},"urlEndpoint":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqa3pvRldraHprZU9CNkRrSVMwYjA3dzdsVkVLd3xBQ3Jtc0tuMG9MOUo4aktGeHRadTZYdUpKM3N3OHNyQl9ObXdKR2dRZWwyMzBtZW15Q1FnUTRuSEJaRmFkbjctUVF2U2VTWGc5cU1DZ0pEblk2ZTE5eDNDeFBnRjlEQ01PeW5udVNFMzhRZlVPX1hpR2ZFRVpNUQ\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jimrohn.com%2F\u0026v=sTzf5UEi4P4","targe